This paper is about sequence labeling for natural language processing, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper proposes a novel search-based probabilistic online learning method for sequence labeling, which involves machine learning and optimization techniques. Therefore, it is likely to also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
